reviewText: will not play in any of my players,. comes up faulty disc. returning it. it got stuck in my one player being my 3rd dvd player. took about 10 minutes to get it out. would like to get it replaced, but no option for that.

Would not play on either player, only show "disc error."  Amazon replaced the disc and the second disc had same exact problem.  No indication on product description that this was a burned disc instead of a pressed disc.  Will not order this product again.
